  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/21e50d29165934b0c451a0a54df2f2fb.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/21e50d29165934b0c451a0a54df2f2fb.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/21e50d29165934b0c451a0a54df2f2fb.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In short, the game is similar to other co-op action games, except this one is about architecture. Explore the level, craft the necessary building materials, and order workers to build. You can play alone or with friends up to 4 players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Being architect is easy</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/b114bbad3903ee65f0d42d0a67b22c38.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/b114bbad3903ee65f0d42d0a67b22c38.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/b114bbad3903ee65f0d42d0a67b22c38.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Examine the design plan, gather resources, give the order to build, and repeat. It is that easy! Once you get familiar with the basics, be ready to learn more about the craft of architecture.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of architecture</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/9a207c57c4133a4d83542e2ddf3dc6fd.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/9a207c57c4133a4d83542e2ddf3dc6fd.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/9a207c57c4133a4d83542e2ddf3dc6fd.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will visit construction sites of 7 different eras:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Ancient Egypt </li><li> Ancient Greece and Ancient Rome </li><li> Ancient Asia </li><li> European Middle Ages </li><li> European Baroque </li><li> European Art Nouveau<br></li><li> American Art Deco  </li></ul><br>Each era contains a multitude of new architectural elements for construction. You can build unique historical buildings by combining them. Besides that each era opens other game mechanics as well. Discover all the architectural secrets!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/5f6efed7b285591c1504c1b39acf0603.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/5f6efed7b285591c1504c1b39acf0603.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/5f6efed7b285591c1504c1b39acf0603.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unlock new crafting recipes to create your own designs. Experiment and combine architectural elements of different styles<br></li><li> Share your creations using the Steam Workshop<br></li><li> Travel through different eras and explore their cultural features through architecture<br></li><li> Use the flexible system for assessing the level progression. Find your own building style</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with friends! </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/915c7190dad5b68ae3aa9eb2b0dcd19a.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/915c7190dad5b68ae3aa9eb2b0dcd19a.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/915c7190dad5b68ae3aa9eb2b0dcd19a.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game will be more fun in coop! Team up with friends to coordinate your actions and build together 4 players coop mode!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/21e50d29165934b0c451a0a54df2f2fb.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/21e50d29165934b0c451a0a54df2f2fb.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/21e50d29165934b0c451a0a54df2f2fb.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In short, the game is similar to other co-op action games, except this one is about architecture. Explore the level, craft the necessary building materials, and order workers to build. You can play alone or with friends up to 4 players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Being architect is easy</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/b114bbad3903ee65f0d42d0a67b22c38.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/b114bbad3903ee65f0d42d0a67b22c38.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/b114bbad3903ee65f0d42d0a67b22c38.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Examine the design plan, gather resources, give the order to build, and repeat. It is that easy! Once you get familiar with the basics, be ready to learn more about the craft of architecture.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of architecture</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/9a207c57c4133a4d83542e2ddf3dc6fd.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/9a207c57c4133a4d83542e2ddf3dc6fd.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/9a207c57c4133a4d83542e2ddf3dc6fd.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will visit construction sites of 7 different eras:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Ancient Egypt </li><li> Ancient Greece and Ancient Rome </li><li> Ancient Asia </li><li> European Middle Ages </li><li> European Baroque </li><li> European Art Nouveau<br></li><li> American Art Deco  </li></ul><br>Each era contains a multitude of new architectural elements for construction. You can build unique historical buildings by combining them. Besides that each era opens other game mechanics as well. Discover all the architectural secrets!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/5f6efed7b285591c1504c1b39acf0603.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/5f6efed7b285591c1504c1b39acf0603.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/5f6efed7b285591c1504c1b39acf0603.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unlock new crafting recipes to create your own designs. Experiment and combine architectural elements of different styles<br></li><li> Share your creations using the Steam Workshop<br></li><li> Travel through different eras and explore their cultural features through architecture<br></li><li> Use the flexible system for assessing the level progression. Find your own building style</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with friends! </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/915c7190dad5b68ae3aa9eb2b0dcd19a.poster.avif?t=1726991731\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/915c7190dad5b68ae3aa9eb2b0dcd19a.webm?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565210/extras/915c7190dad5b68ae3aa9eb2b0dcd19a.mp4?t=1726991731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game will be more fun in coop! Team up with friends to coordinate your actions and build together 4 players coop mode!",
